OL,3,CEx-officer reported to NCA over claims
OL,4,Cof grooming gangs cover-up
OL,6,FA former senior West Yorkshire Police
OL,7,Fofficer has been reported to the
OL,8,FNational Crime Agency (NCA) over
OL,9,Fclaims he failed to investigate the
OL,10,Fgrooming of young girls in Bradford.
OL,12,FJohn Piekos, an ex-detective with
OL,13,FGreater Manchester Police, claims the
OL,14,Fofficer dismissed his reports of child
OL,15,Fsexual exploitation at a children's
OL,16,Fhome in the city over fears it would
OL,17,Fstir up racial tensions.
OL,19,FHis calls for an investigation have
OL,20,Fbeen backed by shadow Home Secretary
OL,21,FChris Philp.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
