OL,3,CEx-officer reported to NCA over claims
OL,4,Cof grooming gangs cover-up
OL,6,FThe NCA has confirmed it is looking at
OL,7,Fthe claims, while West Yorkshire
OL,8,FPolice invited Mr Philp to discuss his
OL,9,Fconcerns directly with the force.
OL,11,FMr Piekos, who was working for an anti-
OL,12,Ftrafficking charity in 2010, said he
OL,13,Fcollated evidence that gangs of
OL,14,Flargely South Asian men were targeting
OL,15,Fvulnerable teenagers in Bradford.
OL,17,F"After we surveilled this children's
OL,18,Fhome for three months and saw the
OL,19,Fexploitation that was taking place, we
OL,20,Ftook part in a meeting with a number
OL,21,Fof charities," he said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
