CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F367A1758830044
OL,3,CEx-officer reported to NCA over claims
OL,4,Cof grooming gangs cover-up
OL,6,F"After I showed them our evidence, one
OL,7,Frepresentative said 'well everyone
OL,8,Fknows that's what happens in
OL,9,Fchildren's homes. It goes on up and
OL,10,Fdown the country'.
OL,12,F"I was absolutely stunned because
OL,13,Fthat's an admission that demanded some
OL,14,Fkind of challenge."
OL,16,FMr Piekos says he took his evidence to
OL,17,Fa West Yorkshire officer he had
OL,18,Fpreviously dealt with, but was shocked
OL,19,Fby the response.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
