OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F367A1758830044
OL,3,CEx-officer reported to NCA over claims
OL,4,Cof grooming gangs cover-up
OL,6,F"(He) said to me 'don't you see how
OL,7,Fmuch effort we've put in to build
OL,8,Fracial harmony in this city and the
OL,9,Fproblems we've gone through? And your
OL,10,Factions are likely to cause it all to
OL,11,Fburn to the ground'.
OL,13,F"I said 'this is about child sexual
OL,14,Fabuse not about racial tension'."
OL,16,FHe claims he was told to "go away and
OL,17,Fleave us alone".
OL,19,FMr Philp has urged the NCA to launch a
OL,20,Fmisconduct investigation.
