OL,3,CEx-officer reported to NCA over claims
OL,4,Cof grooming gangs cover-up
OL,6,FHe said: "I believe there are clear
OL,7,Fgrounds for the National Crime Agency
OL,8,F` who have been tasked with leading a
OL,9,Fnationwide policing operation into
OL,10,Fthese child rape gangs ` to
OL,11,Finvestigate further.
OL,13,F"I have provided the NCA with the name
OL,14,Fof the former senior police officer
OL,15,Fand full details of John Piekos's
OL,16,Faccount.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
