OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F367A1758830044
OL,3,CEx-officer reported to NCA over claims
OL,4,Cof grooming gangs cover-up
OL,6,F"This also shows exactly why a
OL,7,Fnational statutory inquiry into the
OL,8,Fcover up is needed. Yet three months
OL,9,Fsince the Government's forced u-turn
OL,10,Fno progress has been made. This is
OL,11,Fjust not good enough."
OL,13,FA West Yorkshire Police spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid: "We are aware of a letter sent
OL,15,Ffrom Mr Chris Philp MP to the National
OL,16,FCrime Agency.
OL,18,F"However no formal report has yet been
OL,19,Fmade to us directly, and we would
OL,20,Fencourage Mr Philp to contact us
OL,21,Fregarding this matter."
