OL,4,Cof grooming gangs cover-up
OL,6,FThe NCA added: "We can confirm the
OL,7,Fdirector general has received a letter
OL,8,Fand will respond to Mr Philp in due
OL,9,Fcourse."
OL,11,FIn June the government announced a
OL,12,Fnational inquiry into historic child
OL,13,Fsexual exploitation amid widespread
OL,14,Fpressure. It said any individual and
OL,15,Forganisation which overlooked abuse
OL,16,Fwould be held accountable.
OL,18,FBut there are calls for an independent
OL,19,Finquiry specifically focused on
OL,20,FBradford.
